

Star shooter will have The following:

Start Screen
- No need to create other transition screens until game is complete
- Has Continue (top) and start ( bottom) Will have game name and company logo
Town screen
- Walk around, talk to NPCS, enter shops
- Look at status screen of hero
- Doors to enter other areas
Buy Screen
- UX/UI for buy/sell/leave
- 10 items per screen
- Let cursor go below if more than 10 items to go further odwn the list
- Text box for npc
- Portrait  box for npc
- Yes/No Menu to confirm purchase
- Description box for items
Home Base
- Start next mission
- Screen - Status
- Screen- Level up - Distribute stat points
Equipment Screen:
- Set up bullet slots
- Set up Missile slots
- Set up Armor slots
- Set up Magic slots
- Set up Shield Slots
- Set up Accessory Slots
Battle Screen top/down
- Screen scrolls bottom to top
- Enemies come from any direction but mostly from straight ahead
- Gain exp and money by killing enemies
- Pausing freezes game there is no menu during battles
- When you level up you gain stats
- Every level has a boss
- Every level will have a unique twist
- 90% of screen is battle screen
- 10%  bottom fo screen is player stats
- 3 boxes

- HP/Max HP
- Ki/Max Ki

- Heat - if 0 weapon and shields go offline till cool down
- Shield Meter

- Credits
- Exp current/ Exp next level

Battle Screen Left/Right
- Screen scrolls left to right
- Same as above
- These levels are a low priory and are a special bonus
- None of these levels will have anything special they serve as a break for the player

Iteration 1 of game:
This will have 3 levels
Each level will be unique
Most of this phase is building infrastructure of project
Will need to build about 3 bosses, and 5 Enemies
Each stage will host a unique enemy

All Levels have 3 check points infinite amount of continues for time being
Reloads from auto save
- Auto load should have Continue/Load section
- After load play unique get ready music for 3 seconds
- Keep exp from between loads (ignore anything in docs that may suggest otherwise)

Level 1:
Escort mission
There is a ship that is "attached" to the right side, and your mission is to protect it.

Ship will have its own HP and shields

Enemies - 3
Suicide GLiders
- These creatures lock on to a ship and attack it with a bonzai charge
- Low HP
Bile Spitters - These flying creatures shoot out giant balls at player and can move left to right
- Balls are fast and low width
- Medium HP
Manta Rays
 - Shoots out lightning that has 3 prongs.
 -Slow and wide shots
 - Can fly diagonal left or right up or down
 - High HP
 - Status effect Sield short out - drains shields 100%

Obstacles
-Have a narrow passage at some point

Boss
Stage 1
- Infested ship
- Has 4 compartments
- Destroy 3 to get to inner compartment which starts stage 2 of boss
Stage 2
- Giant eye in compartment
- Fly's around  a little faster
- Can shoot eye bullets and ball splitters which branch into 3

Level 2
- Destroy the undead monster before it absorbs a super nova
- Intense heat is a drain on Ki and power core
- Intense gravity wells decrease speed
- Speed down by 25%
- Ki Drain increase by 10%

Obstacles
- Platforms

Enemies
Same as above +
Platform lasher
- Tentacles that can shoot out across screen to attach to player and drag ship to them
- Medium HP
- Drains ki per hit
- Status element missile lock down

Boss
Stage 1
- Ki Wizard
- Ki burst - Shining blast INSTANT speed but has a preflash as warning
- First breath reaches to bottom of screen and can go left or right SLOW speed

Stage 2
- Rage
- Speed and damage +25%
- Summons an swarm of enemies
- Star waves - stars come at player at high speeds from top and  bottom of screen


Stage 3
Save the Children
A Giant ship full of refugee children was attacked, all the kids are in space pods
- Touch the pod and give them a receiver for pickup
- Missing pods will count against player
- 30 pods total
- Can only miss 5 pods
- Player can destroy the pods
- Player can use their ship to protect pods from incoming asteroids

Enemies
- Same as above +

Ball spinner
Defense enemy that has balls spinning you have to kill these to hit core
- high hp
- slow moving
- black out - causes screen to go black for  1 second
- Can shoot a ball to attack player that does not take away from spinnign balls

Obstacles
- Ship Debree so lots of corridors and tight spaces
- Ship pods needs a  ki recharge
- flaming balls that come at player from top of screen dodge or instant shield drain

Boss
Collector
Stage 1
- Can shoot seeker swarms from mouth
- Corrision bile -Ticks HP/Shields Down SLOWLY Thin line breath weapon

Stage 2
- Arms reach down to bottom of screen
- Narrow part of boss fight
- Moves left to right
- Bullet hell

Stage 3
- Boss is hurting arms retract
- Grenade blaster - horizontal line of death pre flash random
- Lurker reinforcement
- Grenade fragments - explosions fragment out

Beams
1 type
Bullets
- Shots bullets from duel linked guns
- Can fire up to 3 shots at a time
- Uses 1 heat per use

Missiles
1 type
seeks nearest enemy
- Uses 10 heat per use

Magic
Shield Ball
- A ball spins around rapidly doing damage to anything it comes into contact with
- This can block all beams
- Has 1 HP
- 20 second duration
- Uses 25 Ki per use
- Have ball flash for final 3 seconds before it vanish

Shield
- Every 1 shield uses 1 heat
- Will Recharge Constantly as long as Shields not max
- If heat is in "cool down" phase then shields will not recharge.
- The higher Heat level the slower shield will recharge
- Every 25 points of Heat equals +1 shield per second

Armor
Father Coat
- High Speed
- High HP
- High Shields
- High Heat

Levels
6 levels 2 per stage
Gain a stat point per level up


Accessory
2 for now
Shield Recharge
- +10% recharge rate
Missile battery
- adds +2 missiles

