Build Player class
- 5 stats
- Power - Increase in HP and Beam Damage
- Magic - Increase in Ki and Magic Damage
- Speed - Increase in Speed and missile damage
- Shield - Increase in Shield max and recharge
- Heat - increase in heat points and recovery time
- HP
- Ki
- Beam Damage
